                  <font color="#00FF00">X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Attack -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Screen -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle, L1, L2, R1 or R2 Buttons</font><br><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BABEL CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character -
                  <font color="#00FF00">D-pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pick piece -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font><br><br>				  
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">CONQUEROR'S CONTINENT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor -
                  <font color="#00FF00">D-pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom in / Zoom out -
                  <font color="#00FF00">Square Button</font><br><br>
&nbsp;</td>
