<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Original mode (Babel) At the title screen, press -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Up(3), Down(5), Right(2), Left. If you entered the code correctly, the title will turn blue.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Control conquerors' faces (Conqueror's Continent) at the conqueror selection screen, hold Select and press -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Up, Down, Left, Right several times. Note: Hold Start to select a conqueror for the CPU to control that character automatically.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Sound test (Conqueror's Continent) at the title screen in original mode, hold Circle and press -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp; Up, Down, Left, Right several times.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; View ending sequence (Conqueror's Continent) at the title screen in original mode, hold Start and press -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Up, Down, Left, Right several times.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Alternate dashboard color (Star Luster) while the title for the original Star Luster is flashing, press -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select, X, Circle, Right, Left, Up, Select, X, Down, Right.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Sound test (Wrestleball) Select "WB League" and "Karate Team" in the original Wrestleball. Then, enter "KWGEN" as a password. Now press -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp; Left or Right to select a song and X to play.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; View all windows visuals (Wrestleball) select "WB League" and "Wrestle Team" in the original Wrestleball. Then, enter -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;"NMURA" as a password.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Screen saver (Wrestleball) Select "WB League" and "Namco Team" in the original Wrestleball. Then, enter -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;"SAITA" as a password. Note: The PlayStation must be reset to return to normal mode.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Bonus points (Wrestleball) Select "WB League" and any standard team in the original Wrestleball. Then, enter -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;"MWAKI" as a password for 995 bonus points.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Bonus teams (Wrestleball) Select any mode in the original Wrestleball. Then at the team selection screen, hold -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X until the four bonus teams appear.</font><br><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Babel - Infinite Power -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>800782EC 0014</font>
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;"MWAKI" as a password for 995 bonus points.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Babel (Classic version) - Infinite Power -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>80100091 0014</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Star Luster - Photon torpedo 99 -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>301F509C 0063</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Star Luster - Photon torpedo deadly blow -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>D0147774 FFFF<br>80147774 0000<br>D0147776 2442<br>80147776 2402</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Star Luster I do not go DATE -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>8018C558 0000</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Star Luster Infinite shield -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>801F50A0 0600</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Star Luster Aircraft repair press L2 -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>D018C538 0001<br>801F50AC 0000<br>D018C538 0001<br>801F50B0 0000<br>D018C538 0001<br>801F50B4 0000</font><br><br>
                  &nbsp;</td>	 
      </tr>
	</table>
